n=as.integer(readline(prompt="Enter the number of elements in the array:"))
nuts=array(0)
Bolts=array(0)
for(i in 1:n){
  nuts[i]=readline(prompt="Enter the value:")
}
for(i in 1:n){
  Bolts[i]=readline(prompt="Enter the value:")
}
bolts=array(0)
for(i in 1:n){
  for(j in 1:n){
    if(nuts[i]==Bolts[j])
      bolts[i]=Bolts[j]
  }
}
print(sort(nuts))
print(sort(bolts))
